author: COMSOL
description: This example examines detailed drug-release kinetics with rate expressions handling drug dissociation/association reactions as well as matrix degradation by enzyme catalysis. The enzyme reaction is described by Michaelis-Menten kinetics. The model investigates design parameters governing the rate of drug release: drug-to-biomaterial affinity, biomaterial degradation, drug loading, and the influence of geometry and composition of the biomaterial matrix.
